Class Movie

  • java.lang.Object
    • Movie

  • public class Movie
extends java.lang.Object
    Each object of this class represents a Movie, and holds attributes such as movieCode (which is a unique identifier), title, status, ageRating, synopsis, cast and director. Also, it holds a list Ratings which created by Customers who watch this movie, through which it derives the value of avgRating
    Author:
    SS3 Group 6
